---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
const lang = 'zh'
---

<Layout
  title="林瑋德醫師｜鈷嵐診所・蘆洲神經科疼痛治療"
  description="林瑋德醫師，神經內科專科，CIPS 認證疼痛超音波醫師，長庚醫院神經科訓練背景，現於鈷嵐診所提供超音波導引注射與再生醫學治療。"
  lang={lang}
  pathname="about"
>

  <section class="fv-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="fv-eyebrow">醫師介紹</p>
      <h1>林瑋德醫師</h1>
      <p class="fv-tagline">神經內科訓練背景・CIPS 認證・超音波導引疼痛治療</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>關於林醫師</h2>
      <p>林瑋德醫師具備神經內科專科、中醫師及疼痛醫學三個領域的訓練背景。在林口長庚紀念醫院神經科完成住院醫師訓練後，結合超音波導引技術與再生醫學，專注於慢性疼痛、神經病變與退化性關節疾病的非手術治療。目前於新北市三重區維德骨科及板橋區生生優動診所執業。</p>
      <p>鈷嵐診所預計 2026 年底於新北市蘆洲區開業，將以疼痛科、再生修復及慢性退化治療為核心。「不只是止痛，而是修復」是林醫師一貫的臨床理念—超音波不只是輔助工具，而是診斷和治療的核心，讓每一針都看得到、打得準。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>專業認證</h2>
      <ul class="about-credential-list">
        <li>
          <span class="credential-title">CIPS 認證疼痛超音波醫師</span>
          <span class="credential-org">World Institute of Pain（WIP）・證號 418</span>
          <a href="https://www.worldinstituteofpain.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">認證機構官網 ↗</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="credential-title">神經內科專科醫師</span>
          <span class="credential-org">台灣神經學學會・證號 001426・有效至 2027 年 12 月</span>
          <a href="https://www.neuro.org.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">台灣神經學學會 ↗</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="credential-title">疼痛醫學專科</span>
          <span class="credential-org">台灣疼痛醫學會・證號 714・有效至 2029 年 3 月</span>
          <a href="https://pain.org.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">台灣疼痛醫學會 ↗</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="credential-title">西醫師・中醫師執照</span>
          <span class="credential-org">衛生福利部・2015 年核發・證號 053036</span>
          <a href="https://ma.mohw.gov.tw/Accessibility/DOCSearch/DOCBasicData?DOC_SEQ=9TE4LdVDm9%252BdmVCAjlafHQ%253D%253D" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">衛福部醫事人員查詢 ↗</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>執業經歷</h2>
      <ul class="about-career-list">
        <li>
          <span class="career-period">2026年底（籌備中）</span>
          <span class="career-title">鈷嵐診所・疼痛科・增生修復・慢性退化</span>
          <span class="career-org">新北市蘆洲區</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="career-period">2025.06 至今</span>
          <span class="career-title">生生優動・疼痛科・增生修復</span>
          <span class="career-org">新北市板橋區</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="career-period">2023.05 至今</span>
          <span class="career-title">維德骨科・疼痛科・增生修復</span>
          <span class="career-org">新北市三重區</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="career-period">2021.03 – 2024.08</span>
          <span class="career-title">重仁診所・神經科・一般科</span>
          <span class="career-org">新北市</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="career-period">2016.08 – 2021.02</span>
          <span class="career-title">林口長庚紀念醫院・神經科住院醫師</span>
          <span class="career-org">桃園市</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>學術發表</h2>
      <ul class="about-publication-list">
        <li>
          <span class="pub-title">Modification of Mechanical Properties, Polymerization Temperature, and Handling Time of Polymethylmethacrylate Cement for Enhancing Applicability in Vertebroplasty</span>
          <span class="pub-journal">BioMed Research International・2016</span>
          <a href="https://doi.org/10.1155/2016/7901562" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">DOI: 10.1155/2016/7901562 ↗</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>外部學術識別</h2>
      <ul class="about-external-list">
        <li>
          <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2380-9104" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">
            ORCID：0000-0003-2380-9104 ↗
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/weide-lin-5268b897/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">
            LinkedIn：Wei-De Lin ↗
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://twmedpro.tw/drlinwate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="credential-link">
            疼痛診聊所・林醫師文章 ↗
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="fv-section fv-cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>有疑問想先諮詢？</h2>
      <p class="fv-reply-note">
        歡迎先透過 LINE 描述症狀，林醫師會幫你初步判斷方向，再決定是否需要進一步評估。
      </p>
      <div class="fv-cta-row">
        <a href="https://line.me/R/ti/p/@twmedpro"
           class="fv-cta fv-cta-line" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          LINE 諮詢
        </a>
        <a href="/zh/first-visit/" class="fv-cta fv-cta-ghost">
          了解初診說明
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
